      "text": "SECTOR ROUTING\nв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓ\nPower Grid в†’ 3005694\nData Center в†’ 3040599\nWater в†’ 3040600\nIndustrial в†’ 3040601\nDefense в†’ 3095136\nDrone DFR в†’ 3103531",
