      "strokeColor": "#ffffff",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fontSize": 18,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "text": "SELF-HEALING LAYER\nв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓв”Ѓ\n\n1. Classify HTTP error code (429 / 401 / 402 / 500 / timeout / connection)\n2. 429 Rate Limit в†’ wait Retry-After header в†’ retry up to 4x\n3. 500 Server в†’ exponential backoff 2s в†’ 4s в†’ 8s в†’ 16s в†’ retry up to 3x\n4. 401 Auth в†’ alert Slack в†’ STOP (key rotation requires redeploy)\n5. 402 Credits в†’ alert Slack в†’ STOP (account top-up required)\n6. Circuit Breaker в†’ 5 consecutive fails в†’ block 5 min в†’ half-open test\n7. Claude Haiku в†’ diagnose root cause + suggest fix в†’ Slack escalation",
      "textAlign": "left"
    },
